title: [Warrior Guild, Glade]
description: A small pond surrounded by tall grass is the perfect spot for meditation and thought.  The sun reflects off the surface of the water, disturbed only slightly by the small afternoon breeze.  A solitary frog sits amidst an army of lily pads, content to bask in the daytime heat.

A small pond surrounded by tall grass is the perfect spot for meditation and thought.  The moonlight reflects off the surface of the water, disturbed only slightly by the gently evening breeze.  A few fireflies flitter over the pond, evidently in no hurry to reach their destination.
